HEADWORD: Garancin
<hw>Gar"an*cin</hw> <pr>(?; 104)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>garance</ets> madder, LL. <ets>garantia</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>An extract of madder by sulphuric acid. It
